Package: auxvecLASSO
Title: LASSO Auxiliary Variable Selection and Auxiliary Vector Diagnostics
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Gustaf", 
        family = "Andersson", 
        email = "gustaf.andersson@scb.se", 
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides tools for assessing and selecting auxiliary variables using LASSO. 
    The package includes functions for variable selection and diagnostics, facilitating 
    survey calibration analysis with emphasis on robust auxiliary vector selection.
